 guys the wrong address for the board meetings=3F Or, at least, you can fre=
eze=C2=A0out the new directors a bit: They are formally in charge of the co=
mpany, but you are=C2=A0<em>actually=C2=A0</em>in charge of the company, an=
d if they ask to review documents or meet with your division heads you can =
just ignore them. The employees are loyal to you, not them.</p><p style=3D"=
margin: 16px 0;">But if you do that, the shareholders might get even more a=
