rm that tries as hard as Qatalyst. Firing up our enforcement machinery ever=
y couple years to haul the industry in for headline-making penalties will n=
ot make people perfect, so firms will continue to discover violations of fi=
rm policies. We cannot enforce to perfection, but there is a way to achieve=
 better compliance.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Qatalyst h=
